# Background Images Required

Place UK city night images here (WebP format, 1080px wide minimum):

- manchester_night.webp (default)
- leeds_night.webp
- portsmouth_night.webp
- birmingham_night.webp
- edinburgh_night.webp
- bristol_night.webp
- newcastle_night.webp

Pre-process images:
- Reduce saturation 30-40%
- Add subtle blue tint
- Ensure dark, moody feel (not bright/colorful)

Rotates daily for variety.
